lemma ldistinct_Lazy_llist [code]: "ldistinct (Lazy_llist xs) = (case xs () of None \<Rightarrow> True | Some (x, ys) \<Rightarrow> x \<notin> lset ys \<and> ldistinct ys)"
by(auto split: llist.split)
